{
  "stem": "10768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was considered a very odd-- they call it a [NON-ENGLISH], a peculiar man.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But he, he was a bachelor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Irene, Irene was married, but apparently he sympathized her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He liked her very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was a extraordinary, lovely person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "This Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was not in our town at the time when the war started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was Sambor, where we had a brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So Irene said, instead of staying in this school on the floor, I will go where Dr.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is with his brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she was there with her husband, her nephew, and her niece.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But at the same time, when she heard-- she knew where in the school we are-- she came to see me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I told her, you know Irene, we are going to be sent somewhere on the Russian territory, possibly that very deep.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So her words to me were, look, my mother and the three sisters are in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "If it were up to me, I would come here and go together with you and everybody else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I don't know what my husband will say, and the nephew, because they have their parents and their family in Lesko.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But I will talk it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I hope that they will decide, and I will join you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Well, they put us on the cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And in the middle of the night, we started.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was a beautiful night in, in June.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I looked, and I looked, looked, if Irene is coming with her husband and with her nephew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But they didn't come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Irene, her husband, her nephew remain there in Sambor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And we were sent on to the Russian territory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I want to just mention about Irene.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She stayed there as soon as the German went.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
